{"tid":1847503,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登預言家：放晒d大陸狗今日落返黎，就會封關了","createTime":"2020-01-28T05:36:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T05:49:34.000Z","uid":73915,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"904f5babd24e905f52b3e7a4abb124c65ec55cd7","tid":1847503,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:36:42.000Z","msg":"跟手就社區爆發<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"660593ac8f8fbf49ebf73568006e4ee638895ebf","tid":1847503,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:37:47.000Z","msg":"劇本已準備好"},{"pid":"8bff01aa14e14fbe327ef57074d1d45a33cd1a14","tid":1847503,"uid":126621,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:38:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5M3ShVs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5M3ShVs.png&h=9ebbd210&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2e9263baa756c97004507d4b53097ca2d1bc14b6","tid":1847503,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:38:34.000Z","msg":"疫埠<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fae531cb55791b63f9d745075d5555b8719a7de","tid":1847503,"uid":213877,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:39:32.000Z","msg":"用個腦都知啦<br />\n<br />\n過多排傳撚到成個香港都係疫港<br />\n<br />\n外國禁香港人入境，香港就類似武漢咁封關<br />\n<br />\n講到底，我懷疑係特撚登"},{"pid":"8fa9ca594a45f0afd2599efe2abe3bdbc182bcfb","tid":1847503,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:40:09.000Z","msg":"所以我一直都講，有錢既香港人趁外國未禁香港人入境前<br />\n<br />\n早早走啦"},{"pid":"857b52a998865076f7e8af76709ac416458fbb9c","tid":1847503,"uid":345593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:41:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"07867b825491471393ac38340c38432f6a577084","tid":1847503,"uid":70417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:42:33.000Z","msg":"醫護罷工前一日封關<br />\n收晒大陸人入醫院，指定診所<br />\n叫番公務員番工，叫私人公司睇齊"},{"pid":"bf5127fb10c64bce71b151092917ba5769ddfc92","tid":1847503,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:42:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">[事關重大請廣傳]</span></span><br />\n<br />\n香港人以及醫護、海關等要職唔一齊三罷嘅後果，只會鼓勵更多支那感染者衝嚟香港求醫，間接促成社區爆發，害死包括醫護同海關全家在內嘅更多人<br />\n<br />\n我會支持三罷，亦會身體力行一齊三罷保護香港，直至港府落實封關<br />\n<br />\n大家唔通想犧牲香港200萬手足同自己全家條命去救呢d準備落地獄嘅人渣？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「感染的人越多越好」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aMf1RYs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaMf1RYs.jpg&h=d189414d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">把我臉上的口罩撕下來朝我吐了口吐沫，說「我活不了，你們都別想活」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XkLMVDM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXkLMVDM.jpg&h=058fd92f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">撕扯她們的防護服<br />\n「要死一起死」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i7qtpw7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi7qtpw7.jpg&h=11a8b2cc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"feca5bd482f259bfd42c891795571bca44cc28e0","tid":1847503,"uid":152422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:48:33.000Z","msg":"民建聯拉隊去左搵林奠，你睇佢今日會唔會宣布然後民建聯就拉banner 成功爭取"},{"pid":"143fcc76649807f5aee86e99c1e525e35297e126","tid":1847503,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:49:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}